er af).<br>
<br>
Overspeccing the weapon spec increases your weapon skill but doesn't change the variance.  As such your damage will go up, but the 50-51 spec change in the damage will not be as large as the 49-50 spec change in damage was (on a level 50).  Testing indicates that overspeccing levels are worth roughly half in terms of damage added. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=36.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=36.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=36.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=36.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.threadControl?topicID=36.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=36.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=36.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub79.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump 